<br>
One has to have a much higher level of aggro than everyone else or prox aggro will make it go after another person. One has to have room to do it in it, and the mob has to be able to move to where you want it to go or else it will go after another person. One needs to be mindful of other mobs aggro and pathing or else they will get adds. <br>
<br>
<br>
